  <brief_title>QOL, ADL and Pain Before and After Intervention With N3 From Krill With D3.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Survey of Chronic Pain Patients' Self-rated Quality of Life, ADL Function and Pain Before and After Intervention With Omega 3 Fatty Acids From Krill With Vitamin D3</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hospitalet Valdemar</agency>
